%a.dropdown-toggle.lead.small{href: "#", 'data-toggle': "dropdown", role: "button", 'aria-haspopup': "true", 'aria-expanded': "false"}
  - if !params[:sort_by]
    = t('sort_books.asc_title')
  - else
    = t("sort_books.#{params[:sort_by]}")
  %i.fa.fa-angle-down.dropdown-icon.pull-right
%ul.dropdown-menu
  - CategorySortingService::SORT_BOOKS.each do |key, value|
    %li
      = link_to t("sort_books.#{key}"), category_path(sort_by: key, page: @pagy.page)
